contacts.message: I'm interested in discussing potential collaboration opportunities for AI integration projects. Your background in ML and full-stack development aligns well with our current needs.
We're looking for a software engineer to join our cloud architecture team. Your experience at Microsoft and AI focus caught our attention. Would love to discuss potential opportunities.
